  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Patients after kidney transplantation received immunosuppression by Tacrolimus, MMF and
      steroids. In one half of the patients after 7 weeks MMF was reduced by half, and after 12
      weeks it was stopped. For the others MMF remained at initial dose.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
